'''Espérance Nyirasafari''' ni umunyamategeko akaba n'umunyapolitiki mu [[Rwanda]], akaba umwe muri ba Visi Perezida ba Sena y'u [[Rwanda]], guhera ku ya 17 Ukwakira 2019.  Yashyizweho muri Sena na Perezida w'u [[Rwanda]], ku ya 22 Nzeri 2019. 

Mbere yibyo, yabaye [[Inama y’Abaminisitiri|minisitiri]] muri Minisiteri ya Siporo n’umuco, kuva ku ya 18 Ukwakira 2018,  kugeza ku ya 22 Nzeri 2019.  Mbere yibyo, kuva 5 Ukwakira 2016 kugeza 18 Ukwakira 2018, yari Minisitiri w’uburinganire n’iterambere ry’umuryango. 

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Espérance yavukiye mu [[Rwanda]] ku babyeyi  babanyarwanda; bombi bishwe muri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|Jenoside yo mu Rwanda]] mu 1994, akiri muto. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2009, yabaye umunyamabanga uhoraho muri minisiteri y’ubutabera mu [[Rwanda]].  Igihe yashyirwaho na minisitiri, ku ya 5 Ukwakira 2016, bivugwa ko yari umwe mu bagize [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|Inteko ishinga amategeko y'u Rwanda]] .  Yasimbuye [[Diane Gashumba]] aba minisitiri muri Migeprof, wabaye Minisitiri w’ubuzima mu [[Rwanda]].  Mu ivugurura ry’abaminisitiri ryo ku ya 31 Kanama 2017, Espérance Nyirasafari yagumanye inshingano ze muri Migeprof.  Nka minisitiri  ashyigikiye kubahana hagati y’abashakanye kugira ngo bateze imbere umuryango. 

== Umuntu ku giti cye ==
Espérance Nyirasafari numubyeyi wubatse. 
